org.beryx.streamplify.product

Class CartesianProduct

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.beryx.streamplify.StreamableProxy<int[],CartesianProduct>
      • org.beryx.streamplify.product.CartesianProduct
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Streamable<int[],CartesianProduct>

    public class CartesianProduct
extends StreamableProxy<int[],CartesianProduct>
    A Streamable providing streams of cartesian product tuples.
    This class is a proxy that delegates to either LongCartesianProduct or BigIntegerCartesianProduct, depending on the cardinalities of the input sets.
